SAN FRANCISCO -- TRANSPORTATION; TRAFFIC MANAGEMENT; COMMISSIONER OF BASEBALL; 
VINCENT, FRANCIS T JR (FAY); OAKLAND A'S (BASEBALL TEAM); SAN FRANCISCO GIANTS 
(BASEBALL TEAM); STADIUMS; CANDLESTICK PARK; OAKLAND COLISEUM; PROPERTY DAMAGE; 
NIMITZ FREEWAY; EVACUATIONS; NORTHERN CALIFORNIA -- FEDERAL AID; SAN FRANCISCO 
-- FEDERAL AID; DEMOLITION; DISASTER RELIEF; DISASTER VICTIMS 
</P>
